subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Lindsay Davenport will withdraw from the Australian Open because she is pregnant with her second child. Davenport, a three-time Grand Slam singles champion and former No. 1-ranked woman, gave birth to a son in June 2007. She returned to the tour, although she has not played since the United States Open last August.
